name: HealthInsuranceCoverageStatusInterventionsSNOMEDCT
title: Health Insurance Coverage Status Interventions SNOMED CT
purpose: (Clinical Focus: <insert metadata> The terms in this value set represent the interventions associated with Health Insurance Coverage Status as identified by the Gravity Project),(Data Element Scope: Supports the exchange of data for the Gravity SDOH Clinical Care FHIR Implementation Guide as well as other uses of these SDOH terms),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes SNOMED CT interventions that have been identified through the Gravity Project community consensus voting process),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes social determinants of health general interventions used in multiple domains)
